    "The commercial models are accessed through their official APIs.",
    "Evaluation metric.",
    "Following existing research [24,54,55], we adopt the widely-used relaxed correctness [54], which requires exact matches for text responses but allows 5% error for numerical responses.",
    "Prompt settings.",
    "The CQA evaluation requires the model to answer with a single word or short phrase."
